# Fuzz - live fight box (Bun + TS) and thin helper (Python) per ADR-0001, PRD #1, issue #2
# See CONTEXT.md for all glossary. No private Memory or data is ever persisted.

# Bun / TypeScript (live fight box)
box/node_modules/
box/.bun/
box/dist/
box/.cache/
*.tsbuildinfo

# Python (thin helper)
helper/__pycache__/
